text:
🥚🥚Attention all egg lovers! 🥚🥚

We have a special game just for you! How to win? It’s very simple, just stop the egg within the blank space. It is as easy as it sounds. Here are the terms and conditions. 🥳🥳🥳

1. Both the Eggs must be stopped within the blank space. No cheating!

2. Take a screen shot and show it to our staffs to claim your free Onsen egg or Ajitsuki tamago

3. Only 1 redemption per screenshot and only available for in-store purchases

4. Redemption will only be applicable with a minimum purchase of 1 Don

5. This promotion will last from 14 Feb 2022 to 21 Feb 2022! So, hurry down and play our game to win your free egg on us! 🤤🤤🤤

Oh and bring your Valentine’s date too 😉

*Available at both our Marine Parade and Punggol store*

text:
Let us bring you behind the scenes and show you what happens when we prepare our Beef Sukiyaki Short Plate Don! All our dons are freshly prepared upon order to ensure that every bowl has the same consistency and taste! 🤤🤤🤤

Step 1: We will place our short plate into our sukiyaki base to cook, whilst the chef prepares the soften onions on the pan!

Step 2: Once the sukiyaki beef is cooked to perfection we mix the onions together to create a mixture of sweet and soft textures and flavours.

Step 3: We will first start with overlaying the rice with the beef and onions.

Step 4: Last but not least before serving, we will crack one Onsen egg over the bowl to give the bowl a creamy and silky texture to the don! We will drizzle the dons with our homemade sauce followed by garnishing with furikake and freshly chopped Green onions!

At Fúkudon, we take pride in providing a hearty and well prepared don while not losing out on quality and taste! Just like home cooked food, it will leave your tummies and hearts satisfied! Come down to any of our stores to try our Beef Sukiyaki Short Plate Don now! 🥳🥳🥳

text:
🐯🧧 Let us usher in a Roarsome Lunar New Year this year with 2 special creations from Fúkudon!
Our favourite local dishes with a twist, the Chilli Crab Salmon Don & Salted Egg Chicken Karaage! 🥳

🌶Chili Crab Salmon Don 🦀
A Singapore dish we all know and love, a mixture of our homemade rempah and our seafood stock.
Not forgetting the balance between tomato ketchup and chilli sauce, this is definitely a classic flavour that you don’t want to miss! Did we mention that real crab meat is also used in this dish?
Paired with a refreshing salad, giving it an extra crunch to the donburi!

🥚Salted Egg Chicken Karaage🍗

We use locally sourced Salted Egg to dress our home-made Chicken Karaage, paired with the creaminess of the milk and a hint of spice from the chilli padi, a match made in heaven! We are sure it will leave you craving for more after the first bite!

Available exclusively at our Punggol outlet only.
Limited portions daily from 27th January (Thursday) onwards, so come on down to 660A Edgedale Plains to get it before it’s gone! 🔥

For pre-orders, you may contact us via Whatsapp at 87878755/ 96350148!📞

🧧Introducing to you our Roaring Combo this Lunar New Year! 🐯

The Roaring Combo consists of 1 Chili Crab Salmon Don & 1 Salted Egg Chicken Karaage for only $18!! 🦀🥚🍗🤤

2 popular dishes loved by all Singaporeans. A mouth-watering combination of sweet, sour from the homemade chili crab sauce and the creaminess from the salted egg chicken karaage. Every bite guarantees an explosion of deliciousness. 😋

Starting from the 27th Jan to the 13th Feb, with limited portions daily, come grab it while you can! 😉

📞For any pre-orders, please contact us at 87878755/ 96350148 via Whatsapp now!

text:
Take a look at our Shoyu Glazed Salmon Don, a signature in both our Marine Parade and Punggol outlets!

At fukudon, we only use Norwegian salmons, that are of the highest quality. Norwegian salmons have a distinct flavour as well as packed with nutrients! Our salmons are cooked in our seasoned flour before it is tossed into our shoyu sauce, where its cooked to perfection!

Our sauce is a mixture of mirin and shoyu (Japanese Soy Sauce), a perfect mix of Sweet and Savoury while exhibiting a hint of saltiness. Accompanied with an onsen egg and our in house tomato salad, incorporating a mixture of locally grown tomatoes, with Japanese cucumbers, onions and orange, topped off with roasted sesame dressing and furikake. A combination worth trying!

Come on down to any of our locations to give our Shoyu Glazed Salmon Don a try! We hope to see you guys soon!

text:
A unique take on our classic Chicken Karaage, the Crunchy Chilli Chicken Karaage! Expertly marinated with Chinese chilli oil to give the Karaage a hint of Spice and Sourness. A perfect side to our Dons! 🌶🌶🌶

To ensure that our Karaages still maintain its juicy inside and crunchy outside, all Chilli Karaages will be made upon order. So don't worry, we ensure that it is the good ol' karaage we are all familiar with! 🤤🤤🤤

Our Chilli Chicken Karaage is only available at our Punggol Outlet. If we have an overwhelming request, we might bring it to Marine Parade. So for all our Punggol Friends, make sure to try the Crunchy Chilli Karaage! We
hope to see you soon! 🥳🥳🥳

text:
Simple but mouth-watering is the perfect way to describe our homemade Chicken Karaage! Juicy yet crunchy, our karaage retains its crispiness while not losing the natural juiciness of the chicken thigh. 🤤🤤🤤

A staple in any Japanese meal, we have put our own twist to this very homely dish by accompanying it with our very own curry sauce. Our curry sauce is packed with flavours and scents from the ingredients that are sourced locally! 🥳🌶🥳

Our Chicken Karaage is available at both our Marine Parade and Punggol Outlets! Don't miss out the karaage
when you visit our stores! We hope to see you soon! 😁😁😁

text:
Aburi Miso Salmon Don w/ Pickled Cucumber, Caramelised Onion & Onsen Egg // $8.20

We bring to you our new BlackBoard dish, Miso Salmon Aburi Don.

A special blend of homemade Miso sauce. By using yellow miso from Japan, the soybean enhances and elevates the Salmon to a whole new different level. You will get to discover the depth of the soybean paste with the perfectly cooked salmon.

The richness of the miso paste is balanced with our accompanying sides, the sweet caramelised onion, and our homemade pickled cucumber!

So come on down and give this special creation a try, a unique dish curated by our chefs in Fúkudon!
Exclusively available at our Marine Parade location!

text:
Merry Christmas and Happy Holidays to all from Fúkudon!
As a way of welcoming in the festive season this year, we will be having a special promotion just for you!

From 23rd December dinner to 24th December lunch, grab 1+1 donburi for $12 nett at our Marine Parade outlet and $13 nett at our Punggol outlets.

To enjoy this promotion:
1. Follow @fukudonsg on either Instagram or Facebook
2. Like & share this post
3. Show it to our staff before purchasing

Just as simple as that, so wait no more and head on down to our stores to enjoy this promo!
Share the joy with our bowls of happiness! 🎄🎁🎅🏻

text:
We have heard you!
A popular blackboard menu item at our flagship outlet is here to stay at our new Punggol outlet!

The Wagyu Onigiri Don, a great infusion of quality and homeliness will be on the menu permanently at Punggol!

Our wagyu is cooked to the perfect doneness, so to not lose its flavour and tenderness. Accompanied by our soy marinated soft boiled egg and our home-made pickled cucumber as a palate cleanser. We are sure it will leave you craving for more!

Come down to our new outlet on the 13th December to give our Wagyu Onigiri Don a try!

text:
A fan favourite, our Chicken Oyakodon is the perfect combination of sweet and savoury.

This dish is the best introduction to donburis.
Soft fluffy eggs atop a layer of rice, served with soft onions & not forgetting the star of the show - Breaded Chicken Breast!

We cannot wait for you guys to come down to our stores to try our Chicken Oyakodon!

text:
Satay Pork Collar Onigiri, Homemade Achar and Onsen Egg. Beautifully garnished with strings of Golden Egg Floss. [$8.60]

In this week’s blackboard, we bring to you satay on rice. Combining a locally familiar Singapore dish into our donburi. Balanced with a homemade achar made with the freshest vegetable and fruits from our very own 84 Marine Parade Market.

Definitely a bowl worth trying!
So come down to Fukudon now to get it before it is gone! 😋✌🏻

Limited portions daily from Tuesday (19th Oct) onwards, so come grab them while you can!! 🍤

// Wagyu Don with Soy Soft Egg & Pickled Cucumber [$11.90] //

Marinated Wagyu Oyster Blade sourced from local Huber’s Butchery, cooked to perfect doneness. Served with a soy-marinated soft boiled egg and a side of crunchy pickled cucumber as a palate cleanser. Makes you yearn for more and more after each mouth.

Limited portions everyday, so come grab it while you can!

text:
It's always a delightful moment when neighboring vendors come to eat at our stall! Da Jie from the Noodle Shop tried our Chicken Don Buri today and expressed great enjoyment from the burst of flavors! She is from mainland China so trying Fúkudon’s dish as a new cuisine is something exciting for her and we are proud to be a part of her foodie journey!

#Fukudonsg
#Donburi
#Hawkerculture
#foodiesg
